title: Rajpoute
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. As of June 2013, there are no vegetarian restaurants in the city, but several vegan options are available here, including baingun bharta, okra, bhindi, chana masala, aloo palak and aloo gobi. Located in the students neighborhood. Casual atmosphere.
